(2. WHAT NORMIES WANT) show newline
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(    What they have now:          What they actually want:) show newline
(    --------------------         ------------------------) show newline
(    iCloud                       My stuff, always there) show newline
(    Photos app                   My pictures, forever) show newline
(    Notes                        My recipes, shareable) show newline
(    Messages                     Talk to people I trust) show newline
() show newline
(They don't want a distributed cryptographic vault. They want:) show newline
() show newline
